msgid "So evamāha:"
msgstr "They say:"

msgctxt "dn1:106.2"
msgid "‘antavā ayaṃ loko parivaṭumo."
msgstr "‘The cosmos is finite and bounded."

msgctxt "dn1:106.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu?"
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "dn1:106.4"
msgid ""
"Ahañhi ātappamanvāya padhānamanvāya anuyogamanvāya appamādamanvāya "
"sammāmanasikāramanvāya tathārūpaṃ cetosamādhiṃ phusāmi, yathāsamāhite citte "
"antasaññī lokasmiṃ viharāmi."
msgstr ""
"Because by dint of keen, resolute, committed, and diligent effort, and right "
"focus I experience a samādhi of the heart of such a kind that I meditate "
"perceiving the cosmos as finite."

msgctxt "dn1:106.5"
msgid "Imināmahaṃ etaṃ jānāmi:"
msgstr "Because of this I know:"

msgctxt "dn1:106.6"
msgid "“yathā antavā ayaṃ loko parivaṭumo”’ti."
msgstr "“The cosmos is finite and bounded.”’"

