msgctxt "dn1:109.1"
msgid ""
"Tatiye ca bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā kimāgamma kimārabbha antānantikā antānantaṃ "
"lokassa paññapenti?"
msgstr "And what is the third ground on which they rely?"

