"uddhamadho antasaññī lokasmiṃ viharāmi, tiriyaṃ anantasaññī."
msgstr ""
"Because by dint of keen, resolute, committed, and diligent effort, and right "
"focus I experience a samādhi of the heart of such a kind that I meditate "
"perceiving the cosmos as finite vertically but infinite horizontally."

msgctxt "dn1:110.10"
msgid "Imināmahaṃ etaṃ jānāmi:"
