"vināsaṃ vibhavaṃ paññapenti sattahi vatthūhi."
msgstr ""
"There are some ascetics and brahmins who are annihilationists. They assert "
"the annihilation, eradication, and extermination of an existing being on "
"seven grounds."

msgctxt "dn1:175.2"
msgid ""
"Te ca bhonto samaṇabrāhmaṇā kimāgamma kimārabbha ucchedavādā sato sattassa "
"ucchedaṃ vināsaṃ vibhavaṃ paññapenti sattahi vatthūhi?"
msgstr "And what are the seven grounds on which they rely?"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="152"></a>
#. VAR: evaṃdiṭṭhi → evaṃdiṭṭhī (bj, pts1, mr)
msgctxt "dn1:176.1"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco samaṇo vā brāhmaṇo vā evaṃvādī hoti evaṃdiṭṭhi:"
msgstr "There are some ascetics and brahmins who have this doctrine and view:"

msgctxt "dn1:176.2"
msgid ""
"‘yato kho, bho, ayaṃ attā rūpī cātumahābhūtiko mātāpettikasambhavo kāyassa "
"bhedā ucchijjati vinassati, na hoti paraṃ maraṇā, ettāvatā kho, bho, ayaṃ "
"attā sammā samucchinno hotī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘This self is physical, made up of the four primary elements, and produced "
"by mother and father. When it’s annihilated and destroyed when the body "
"breaks up, and doesn’t exist after death, that’s how this self becomes "
"rightly annihilated.’"

msgctxt "dn1:176.3"
msgid "Ittheke sato sattassa ucchedaṃ vināsaṃ vibhavaṃ paññapenti."
msgstr "That is how some assert the annihilation of an existing being."

msgctxt "dn1:176.4"
msgid "(1: 51)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="153"></a>
msgctxt "dn1:177.1"
msgid "Tamañño evamāha:"
msgstr "But someone else says to them:"

msgctxt "dn1:177.2"
msgid "‘atthi kho, bho, eso attā, yaṃ tvaṃ vadesi, neso natthīti vadāmi;"
msgstr "‘<em>That</em> self of which you speak does exist, I don’t deny it."

msgctxt "dn1:177.3"
msgid "no ca kho, bho, ayaṃ attā ettāvatā sammā samucchinno hoti."
msgstr "But that’s not how <em>this</em> self becomes rightly annihilated."

msgctxt "dn1:177.4"
msgid "Atthi kho, bho, añño attā dibbo rūpī kāmāvacaro kabaḷīkārāhārabhakkho."
msgstr ""
"There is another self that is divine, physical, sensual, consuming solid "
"food."

msgctxt "dn1:177.5"
msgid "Taṃ tvaṃ na jānāsi na passasi."
msgstr "You don’t know or see that."

msgctxt "dn1:177.6"
msgid "Tamahaṃ jānāmi passāmi."
msgstr "But I know it and see it."

msgctxt "dn1:177.7"
msgid ""
"So kho, bho, attā yato kāyassa bhedā ucchijjati vinassati, na hoti paraṃ "
"maraṇā, ettāvatā kho, bho, ayaṃ attā sammā samucchinno hotī’ti."
msgstr ""
"When this self is annihilated and destroyed when the body breaks up, and "
"doesn’t exist after death, that’s how this self becomes rightly annihilated.’"

